    "Loans are an essential part of the financial ecosystem, and in the DeFi platforms, it is possible to lend and borrow crypto assets without KYC procedures\", p.11 6 Caldarelli and Ellul [17] Deposits & loans \"Collateralized loans are loans given after the borrower locks a predetermined amount of assets.",
    "\", p.11 6 Caldarelli and Ellul [17] Deposits & loans \"Flash loans are a particular form of loans that are only possible thanks to the implementation of smart contracts.",
    "[…] It consists of a particular form of contract in which the loan is taken and repaid simultaneously [72].",
    "That way, the illiquidity, and the default risks are denied.\"",
    "P.11 6 Caldarelli and Ellul [17] Exchanges \"Automated Market Makers, often referred to as decentralized exchanges, are smart contracts that hold both assets of a trading pair."
